{"tid":21939,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天津警方押醉駕者去殮房「懺悔」","createTime":"2016-12-04T06:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T01:00:38.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"88dfa1b6aa6d64a5bc0997351d5197c5e12ee5f8","tid":21939,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T06:59:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aqwsLBCdxpQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaqwsLBCdxpQ&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqIscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=7da5ece0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aqwsLBCdxpQ</a> <br />\n<br />\n公安再被曝光以「酷刑」對付違反交通規例的人！繼深圳交警要求亂開車頭「遠光燈（港稱高燈）」的司機，瞪眼看燈1分鐘後，天津交警日前開始，將醉酒駕車者送到醫院殮房接受「生命教育」。有受罰者直指現場陰森恐怖，以後不敢再犯例。 <br />\n<br />\n天津交警日前開始「開班」，把酒駕司機載到殮房外醒酒，並且安排他們現場觀看車禍事故影片及接受安全教育；現場陰冷的氣氛，讓酒駕司機嚇得酒都醒了，直說不敢再喝酒開車。 <br />\n<br />\n當地交通警察賈世杰表示，這次選在當地人民醫院殮房前教育酒駕者有特別用意，因為這裡躺著的每一具屍體都是非正常死亡，尤以事故為主。 <br />\n<br />\n現場觀看交通事故影片 <br />\n<br />\n天津交警在官方微博上也寫道：「酒駕不可怕？只是怕被抓？別天真了，等你的不只是值勤的交警，你敢面對因酒駕等交通違法行為引發事故的嚴重後果嗎」？ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1545000/1549434/b40039a00915b8d706002b3be90da6bc_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1545000%2F1549434%2Fb40039a00915b8d706002b3be90da6bc_1024.png&h=8ceb3212&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1545000/1549434/517456d72b4f675f32b785e1f7591e11_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1545000%2F1549434%2F517456d72b4f675f32b785e1f7591e11_1024.png&h=23259353&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一名酒駕者當場表示後會，說以前總是抱著僥倖心理，這次的教育讓他印象深刻，以後絕不會喝酒開車了。據報道聲稱，酒駕駕駛人到殮房門前接受教育是「自願行為」，且不會進入殮房。 <br />\n<br />\n網民熱議．雖然有人認為將人帶去殮「醒酒」做法似乎太過了，但有不少人十分同意這樣的方式，甚至覺得越嚴厲越好，不然總是有人罰不怕，不見棺材不掉淚正是應用在他們這種人身上。"},{"pid":"2529fe0175ad09f31db946084194294e8bc08d67","tid":21939,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T06:59:48.000Z","msg":"諗起跪車頭燈"},{"pid":"dd1bebdb4eafe5af0546c5be34ccd031788897a6","tid":21939,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07:02:48.000Z","msg":"台擬罰醉駕者清潔殯儀館<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20161113/19832075\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20161113%2F19832075&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqIscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=db4b90c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20161113%2F19832075&h=a29e709b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20161113/19832075</a><br />\n<br />\n咁都要抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 山寨強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f732a6b189d787693d83c428964196abf2729b65","tid":21939,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07:06:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99c2f8f1efc527673491c1377bf315d867e8021b","tid":21939,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07:08:29.000Z","msg":"睇標題仲以為困住佢係殮房"},{"pid":"7ed2a17334cab174171fcd2c1dcb2611ff382f60","tid":21939,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T08:40:16.000Z","msg":"Online"},{"pid":"66c68435377d373eb6bb797c590c8dba72ff443c","tid":21939,"uid":50700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T08:42:04.000Z","msg":"香港都要咁做 太多人揸移動武器"},{"pid":"15e3fa79a4137bad149b63237daeb75ce2e19c34","tid":21939,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T08:44:13.000Z","msg":"呢樣野又幾值得其他地方效法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c32d6dc256277e057c8d1fb20d0c2517db6d27d","tid":21939,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0